snippet.title: Move or Die: Unleashed! OUT NOW ON NINTENDO SWITCH!
snippet.description:
Move or Die: Unleashed is finally available for purchase on Nintendo Switch! Would you believe it?
NA: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/move-or-die-unleashed-switch/
EU: https://www.nintendo.co.uk/Games/Nintendo-Switch-download-software/Move-or-Die-Unleashed-2175557.html
https://moveordiegame.com/
https://thoseawesomeguys.com/
~
Join the Discord Community:
https://discord.gg/moveordie
~
Video Edit by Nicolae (Xelu) Berbece (https://www.youtube.com/c/MentalCheckpoint)
Additional Footage by Dino Katherine (http://trailergoblin.com) 
Voice Over by Mick (Ricepirate) Lauer (https://twitter.com/RicepirateMick)
Music by Jacob Lincke (https://jacob-lincke.com/)

Additional Visuals by Lidia Macov, Aniela Ariton & Paul Paun
Script by Paso & Nicolae (Xelu) Berbece
Producer: Cristian Botea (https://twitter.com/summoningpixels)
Project Manager: Vlad Calu (https://twitter.com/vladwes)
